 T</strong>uscan wine-tasting experience when visiting Italy.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Original</em><strong>: </strong>Symptoms of influenza include fever and nasal congestion.<br />\r\n<em>Paraphrase</em><strong>:</strong> A stuffy nose and elevated temperature are signs you may have the flu.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Original</em><strong>:</strong> The price of a resort vacation typically includes meals, tips and equipment rentals, which makes your trip more cost-effective.<br />\r\n<em>Paraphrase</em><strong>:</strong> All-inclusive resort vacations can make for an economical trip.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Original</em><strong>:</strong> He has tons of stuff to throw away.<br />\r\n<em>Paraphrase</em><strong>: </strong>He needs to get rid of a lot of junk.</li>\r\n</ul>'),(2163,349,'_single_flexible_content_3_single_contents_text','field_5fa5370c65311'),(2164,349,'single_flexible_content_4_single_link_txt_text','link this is title'),(2165,349,'_single_flexible_content_4_single_link_txt_text','field_5fa5372c65313'),(2166,349,'single_flexible_content_4_single_link_txt_url','http://amano.cd/wp-admin/post-new.php?post_type=case'),(2167,349,'_single_flexible_content_4_single_link_txt_url','field_5fa5374465314'),(2168,349,'single_flexible_content_4_single_link_txt_target','a:1:{i:0;s:6:\"_blank\";}'),(2169,349,'_single_flexible_content_4_single_link_txt_target','field_5fa5375c65315'),(2170,349,'single_flexible_content_5_single_link_post_obj','a:2:{i:0;s:1:\"8\";i:1;s:3:\"116\";}'),(2171,349,'_single_flexible_content_5_single_link_post_obj','field_5fa53a67ba04e'),(2172,349,'single_flexible_content_6_single_post_block_obj','a:2:{i:0;s:3:\"116\";i:1;s:1:\"8\";}'),(2173,349,'_single_flexible_content_6_single_post_block_obj','field_5fa53a89ba050'),(2174,349,'single_flexible_content_7_single_product_block_obj','a:1:{i:0;s:3:\"233\";}'),(2175,349,'_single_flexible_content_7_single_product_block_obj','field_5fa53a9eba052'),(2176,349,'single_flexible_c